,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T16:13:43.000Z","msg":"19:大家好 歡迎今晚黎到光明頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n現代左膠當道<br />\n咩大愛呀 難民議題 d所以既評論員觀點令人發笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話說琴日又發生左一d令人唔開心既恐襲...<br />\n燒山：人渣（大叫）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依個世界唔係話拖d人難民出海咁運作<br />\n我將會將你既言論翻譯成19國語言 等世人評擊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係唔可以比依d聲音出現係文明社會<br />\n毓民：我屌你老母啦燒弱元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然19講d言論係偏激 不過你咁撚樣翻譯出街<br />\n比極端組織成員將香港成為襲擊目標係咪你咩飛呀 你老味<br />\n講野都唔經大腦  來我都唔想評論依件事 不過你咁撚樣...<br />\n曾主席：（插嘴）我建議黃議員請你都係講返主題<br />\n有共產黨就唔會有問題 共產黨萬歲 嘿嘿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋乜燒山唔係好推多元聲音架咩 共產黨依方面好似仲文明過你喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大班：喂 曾肉成 你唔好以以做主席就大晒先得架<br />\n康港講垃圾會我冇玩好耐架啦 我想講乜你都唔可以趕我走架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你答我你係味地下黨員先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBili bala...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02fe10752270664721ac4f066bd42b856297c2fd","tid":527421,"uid":137178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c098470ebae63834bc48a4b62ea1bc29f23262c","tid":527421,"uid":21954,"like":71,"dislike":2,"score":69,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T07:36:49.000Z","msg":"坤狗 bobby 田蕊妮 胡鴻鈞 黎明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T16:28:37.000Z","msg":"諗起 笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd1eb9a5affc4bc2a26e51c5f2b99ba69cb51b16","tid":527421,"uid":72955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T16:50:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>坤狗 bobby 田蕊妮 胡鴻鈞 黎明 <img src=\"/ass